Glenn Wichman
.SH BUGS
.PP
Probably infinite
(although countably infinite).
However,
that Ice Monsters sometimes transfix you permanently is
.I not
a bug.
It's a feature.
.PP
We very much welcome rogue5.4 GutHub pull requests
(\fIhttps://github.com/lcn2/rogue5.4/pulls\fP) to fix any
failures to compile, compiler warning messages, and/or program crashes.
.PP
You may also file a rogue5.4 GitHub bug report
(\fIhttps://github.com/lcn2/rogue5.4/issues/new?template=bug_report.md\fP).
